{"tid":2289390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2男警在酒店強姦女子被捕 ！！！！","createTime":"2020-11-17T08:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T09:15:59.000Z","uid":199670,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c10e52ace99d5dca58efc69ac10c5b900d36a84a","tid":2289390,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"警方再度爆出性醜聞。消息稱，早前數名男女警員前往酒吧消遣之後，部份人離開，餘下兩名男警帶同一名女子前往一間酒店租房。事發後，該名女子報案，報稱在酒店內被兩名警員強姦。據悉，警方接報後高度重視，經調查後拘捕兩名男警，案件交由西九龍總區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n兩名涉嫌強姦被捕男警的身份有不同說法，其中一版本指兩名男警同隸屬機動部隊X連，兩人年約20多歲，目前擔任防暴警工作；另一說法則指被捕男警分別隸屬CID及機動部隊。此外，有傳早前往酒吧消遣的男女警之中，尚包括一名來自俗稱O記的有組織罪案及三合會調查科的年長「老差骨」探員，不過這名探員疑最終未有前往酒店，故暫時相信他與案無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201117/IQ266DSLBFAPHNL6G5GHYQRVR4/?fbclid=IwAR3PGZb_GPjxnexDKUXvK2-z5W_QQJhYOpjC651xz1Z8QVzFSeIf7yf9JhE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201117%2FIQ266DSLBFAPHNL6G5GHYQRVR4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3PGZb_GPjxnexDKUXvK2-z5W_QQJhYOpjC651xz1Z8QVzFSeIf7yf9JhE&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=c2fe60fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201117%2FIQ266DSLBFAPHNL6G5GHYQRVR4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3PGZb_GPjxnexDKUXvK2-z5W_QQJhYOpjC651xz1Z8QVzFSeIf7yf9JhE&h=65bf1d59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201117/IQ266DSLBFAPHNL6G5GHYQRVR4/?fbclid=IwAR3PGZb_GPjxnexDKUXvK2-z5W_QQJhYOpjC651xz1Z8QVzFSeIf7yf9JhE</a>"},{"pid":"e92ee62a0c97f34a91eced365a8f298f1902a5ea","tid":2289390,"uid":199670,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySYQMqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySYQMqP.png&h=19026145&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba13c90265e055572d6eeeb0094f6af8599d0435","tid":2289390,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img s